game.name: Halloween Party Cake
game.description:
Two beautiful women Elsa and Anna are ready to bring more fun and entertainment for you in this awesome, free online gaming activity - Halloween Party Cake. As the name of this popular cooking game suggests, you have to prepare a delicious Halloween Party Cake under the supervision of these two cute girls. Try to be very careful and focus on the major instructions in order to win this highly challenging and exciting kids game. Everything right from the graphics to gaming control is awesome. You will surely enjoy each level of this cool cooking game.

Halloween is right here and both the princesses Anna and Elsa are pretty excited to get themselves ready for a big event. In this flash girls game, you do not only dress up these gorgeous girls, but you also have to take the responsibility of preparing a delicious Halloween Party Cake. You will be provided with an extensive range of awesome clothes to adorn these two beautiful Disney Frozen sisters. Lots of scrumptious ingredients and tools are also there to help you create a mouth-watering cake. Do not forget to earn the points in this fabulous game designed for girls. 

You can play this free online cooking game alone or with your friends and have huge fun while sitting on one place. Use your knowledge about the current fashion trends, cooking skills, creativity and patience to get both the tasks done timely. The quicker you will perform your jobs, the higher points you will be able to earn.
